{"tid":858674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lego林鄭倒錢落海","createTime":"2018-10-12T03:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T03:48:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"101c589c6b2e0a674fb00814d8fc100adffd6807","tid":858674,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181012/20520540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F20520540&d=z5r78ieZp71fnBT0IHEi3QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f2fca2ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F20520540&h=acdc5e95\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181012/20520540</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月12日 <br />\n<br />\nLego林鄭倒錢落海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181012/large/1539277905_21c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539277905_21c0.jpg&h=3fb31fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】「明日大嶼」龐大工程估計耗資5,000億元，民意譁然。經常用Lego積木攝製社會場景的攝影師Ric Tse即興模擬特首林鄭月娥倒錢落海，憑此寄意。他說，香港還有地可以用，無必要花龐大公帑起人工島。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「雖然香港一路都有填海，但如果政府唔改變現時嘅人口政策，再多嘅地都解決唔到住屋問題。再者，前車可鑑，高鐵超支，效益成疑，將來政府嘅大型基建，最終會使幾多錢，無人知。」Ric說。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱藉「玫瑰園」鑑古知今<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n紅隧加價一倍　政府死不修改<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林超英斥低估風暴潮威脅<br />\n<br />\n向內地買海砂料花439億<br />\n<br />\n稱藉「玫瑰園」鑑古知今<br />\n<br />\n紅隧加價一倍　政府死不修改<br />\n<br />\n特首自詡大膽：禁傳統煙有得諗<br />\n<br />\n聶德權稱暫不重啟政改<br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望新低<br />\n<br />\n九價HPV疫苗　小五女童免費打<br />\n<br />\n產檢毋須假紙可獲有薪病假<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄：普教中交學校決定<br />\n<br />\n天價填海　林鄭卸責規劃署"},{"pid":"0c615ced99a13243bce1f6bd98f0edb58783a669","tid":858674,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"今日小蠢，明日大愚"},{"pid":"7f20edb4a17ccfc3c90ed2da6c886d9db4bca476","tid":858674,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲宣傳要有多啲 <br />\n比fb啲人都意識到"},{"pid":"fb967bac1458625395f78e344daa3ddae6306fd3","tid":858674,"uid":6869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}